Description_lang: Aluriel brands people with the Mark of Frost. Each marked player inflicts $213624s1 Frost damage to allies within $213624A1 yards. Damage taken inflicts the Frostbitten status ailment, increasing damage from Mark of Frost by $212647s2% per application.If two marked players come into contact with another, they will cause an explosion for $212648s1 Frost damage and Mark of Frost will bounce to the closest ally. This effect prefers targets who are not Frostbitten.
AuraDescription_lang: Periodically inflicting Frost damage to nearby allies.Contact with other marked players will cause this effect to bounce.
